      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities (ASTM F1717 bench testing of same device design under same loading mode) are directly relevant to the COU; no extrapolation beyond validated domain required.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the identical device design (non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw) under the identical loading mode (ASTM F1717 compression-bending) as the COU. No interpolation or extrapolation required. Two independent laboratories confirm reproducibility. Achieved level 3."
